{"tid":1319874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚人！高手自製「解壓縮炸彈」能把 46MB 變 4.5PB","createTime":"2019-07-15T09:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T17:58:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":538,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"1915a4cfe0cf80e0ebb607da31f5b45cd85e9693","tid":1319874,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2019/07/15/190715-37385-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2F190715-37385-1.png&h=0e699c41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nZip、RAR 這類「壓縮檔」，是大多數電腦用戶都熟悉的格式，能夠將較大的檔案包裝一個小檔或分割，使得許多網路上的資源經常以這種檔案格式存在。也有一些惡意攻擊選擇以類似的方式下手，讓受害者下載一個相對小得多的檔案，接著因為打開突然爆增的檔案體積，癱瘓用戶的電腦。<br />\n<br />\n因效果類似炸彈，這種攻擊方式也被不少人以「解壓縮炸彈」（Zip Bomb）來描述。<br />\n<br />\n而據外媒《VICE》消息，有趣的是，一名研究員 David Fifield，則展示了一個驚人的「解壓縮炸彈」，能夠將 46MB 小巧壓縮檔，經過解壓縮程序後變成 4.5PB，相當於4,500TB，是足以「轟炸」伺服器主機的等級。去年，David Fifield 的技術還沒那麼驚人，但也能製作出將 42kb 變為 5.5GB 的壓縮檔。<br />\n<br />\n他的早期範例，還有 10MB、但能夠膨脹到 281TB 的「解壓縮炸彈」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，最新的「4.5PB」級炸彈，還需要支援 ZIP64 標準，因此一些舊的電腦並不具備相容性。此外，這項技術文件也僅是在示範新型的解壓縮技術，而非以資安防範這類議題作為主軸。<br />\n<br />\nNew Zip Bomb Stuffs 4.5PB of Data into 46MB File<br />\n<br />\nAs he writes on his blog:<br />\n<br />\n   This article shows how to construct a non-recursive zip bomb whose<br />\n   compression ratio surpasses the DEFLATE limit of 1032. It works by<br />\n   overlapping files inside the zip container, in order to reference a<br />\n  &ldquo;kernel&rdquo;of highly compressed data in multiple files, without making<br />\n   multiple copies of it. The zip bomb&rsquo;s output size grows quadratically<br />\n   in the input size; i.e., the compression ratio gets better as the bomb<br />\n   gets bigger. The construction depends on features of both zip and<br />\n   DEFLATE&mdash;it is not directly portable to other file formats or compression<br />\n   algorithms. It is compatible with most zip parsers, the exceptions<br />\n   being&ldquo;streaming&rdquo;parsers that parse in one pass without first consulting<br />\n   the zip file&rsquo;s central directory."},{"pid":"293df00a49ce46091c11cd05b8c79ac475abc6aa","tid":1319874,"uid":2507,"like":484,"dislike":1,"score":483,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:07:23.000Z","msg":"核彈級裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beac7d31f7538998e5c1953dd40a8a1e3c1607c2","tid":1319874,"uid":32511,"like":516,"dislike":1,"score":515,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"阿蛇個報案系統可以加入zip file?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d05903b9992d51f6660056f089f009cd3cc20c","tid":1319874,"uid":3358,"like":179,"dislike":0,"score":179,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"其實原理係咩<br />\n有冇it人講緊下"},{"pid":"8f510ff4b5dd2f0c1f63f82ab637c34fd227a87f","tid":1319874,"uid":59586,"like":236,"dislike":1,"score":235,"quote":{"pid":"beac7d31f7538998e5c1953dd40a8a1e3c1607c2","tid":1319874,"uid":32511,"like":516,"dislike":1,"score":515,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"阿蛇個報案系統可以加入zip file?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"10MB &gt; 281TB<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214543a411ccd458a7db6bb13acdd9762679c830","tid":1319874,"uid":32511,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"8f510ff4b5dd2f0c1f63f82ab637c34fd227a87f","tid":1319874,"uid":59586,"like":236,"dislike":1,"score":235,"quote":{"pid":"beac7d31f7538998e5c1953dd40a8a1e3c1607c2","tid":1319874,"uid":32511,"like":516,"dislike":1,"score":515,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:07:5